HEADWORD: Birthnight
<hw>Birth"night`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The night in
which a person is born; the anniversary of that night in succeeding
years.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The angelic song in Bethlehem field,⟦br⟧
On thy <qex>birthnight</qex>, that sung thee Savior born.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Birthplace</ent>⟦br⟧
